snippet.title: Starinspired Tutorial: Amber Heard Red Carpet Look
snippet.description:
Inspirationsbilder:
http://misszophie.blogspot.com/2011/11/starinspired-look-amber-heard.html

Trailer zu The Rum Diary:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-m0yqS3jodU

Verwendete Produkte:
Illamasqua Skin Base Foundation SB03
http://www.illamasqua.com/shop/catalogue/category/face/products/new-skin-base-foundation/304/

MAC Studio Sculpt Concealer NC15
Urban Decay Naked Palette: Mischung aus "Buck","Smog" 
http://www.lookfantastic.com/urban-decay-naked-palette-multi/10368656.html

AVON Super Shock Geleyeliner 
Kat von D Ludwig Palette: Lucifer (mattes schwarz)
essence gebackener Lidschatten Nr. 11
essence 2 in 1 Volume Mascara
Flormar Perfect Coverage Concealer 01 Fair
Soleil tan de Chanel Bronzer
alverde Mademoisell Blush 10 Peche (LE)
Catrice Blush "Coral Sand" (leider nicht mehr im Sortiment)
MAC Highlighter Lightscapade (LE)
MAC Lipliner "Boldly Bare"
MAC lipstick "Innocence Beware" (LE)

Oberteil: Zara (alt)
